text: Ebore Canella (born 23 March 1913, date of death unknown) was an Italian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1913 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Italian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Italy Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Genoa
